{"tid":597095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"領展為重新裝修旗下商場，連百佳、榮華都唔放過，慘遭逼走！！","createTime":"2018-03-18T09:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T10:38:42.000Z","uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b4156a640687bdec729edfbb83aad01d5c98716b","tid":597095,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:55:42.000Z","msg":"領展再次「大裝修」，上水彩園廣場地下商戶在3月底前將陸續結業。近期彩園廣場地下多間商舖，包括百佳超級市場、榮華餅家、新台場台灣食品專門店等，均已貼出告示指因租約期滿，即將結束營業。在彩園邨經營30多年的鳳凰粉麵茶餐廳也承認亦將租約期滿，惟仍未和領展商討續租事宜。有街坊憂慮領展會逼走茶餐廳、麵包舖，批評其行為霸道、無良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180317/large/1521297876_0535.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180317%2Flarge%2F1521297876_0535.jpg&h=0fba2d73&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n彩園廣場地下今年二月起多間商戶貼上結業啟示，包括海天堂龜零膏、百佳超級市場、榮華餅家等。鳳凰粉麵茶餐廳負責人亦向本報確認，與領展的合約即將完結，領展指會就合約和其洽商，負責人表示對日後商場狀況不了解，亦拒絕接受訪問。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180316/large/1521211231_498a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180316%2Flarge%2F1521211231_498a.jpg&h=7c57ecb9&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n領展回覆本報指，彩園廣場地下部分樓面計劃今年4月起展開優化工程，透過提升設施及服務，為顧客提供更舒適及多元化的購物體驗，工程期間場內將有超市及食肆繼續提供服務，優化完成後的租務安排將於稍後跟商戶磋商，無回應日後會否大幅加租。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180318/57957370\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57957370&d=XdPyjybqQaprp66llt%2BsRb5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=369ee163\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180318%2F57957370&h=e10c219b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180318/57957370</a>"},{"pid":"755f44609cbd432e4556c010070174021344c7cc","tid":597095,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:56:53.000Z","msg":"曾在彩園邨居住多年的王女士批評領展行為霸道，「地產霸權呀，領展仲衰過私人地產商」，她指彩園邨有不少長者居住，現在多間商舖也結業，老人家需步行到石湖墟才能購買生活所需，「對佢地（長者）嚟講好遠，有困難」，又稱彩園廣場前身為街市，「以前區議員話裝修之後都會有街市，點知得返兩間超市，領展真係好霸道」。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180316/large/1521212600_3d46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180316%2Flarge%2F1521212600_3d46.jpg&h=a212d0c6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n彩園邨居民魏先生擔憂彩園商場地下的茶餐廳和麵包舖會相繼結業，「我由細食到大架，如果結業係唔切合居民需要」，他認為領展無良心，「佢地為賺錢。」陳先生促領展勿趕走彩園邨僅餘的小商戶，反而應該增加與民生相關的店舖，「次次裝修之後都剩番好少選擇，好唔應該。」"},{"pid":"5bba77039af872113cf4fdd70b12b5e97283d1ec","tid":597095,"uid":42820,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T09:58:36.000Z","msg":"裝修都唔比 毒果真係惡過共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90208508dbded1252c06af71a7636cde776e80ee","tid":597095,"uid":35014,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:09:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a68ac73cb3a097289dcda7006314ab9f3060e17a","tid":597095,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:25:44.000Z","msg":"長者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d220e7693ed2b664223f5b71ebffe693f195012b","tid":597095,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:27:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5bd7df1536f256ca35ceb85f57203057ad417f1b","tid":597095,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://sparkpost.files.wordpress.com/2011/10/2604769434481454942.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsparkpost.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F10%2F2604769434481454942.jpg&h=475a2b15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"794d4bfa490bbf1457d345fb73beab2a837331bf","tid":597095,"uid":92479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:36:27.000Z","msg":"何文田都係啦無人提"},{"pid":"92929f79d6cb0e53a477e701c51e3af9ba2d5a30","tid":597095,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}